steps.name: Stage 0: Retrieve a compute node from HSM to be used in later stages
Stage 1: Power the target node on to prepare it for the test case
Stage 2: Poll until the on transition operation has completed
Stage 3: Retrieve the completed on transition data
Stage 4: Verify that the target node is powered on using power-status
Stage 5: Restart the target node with a hard-restart transition
Stage 6: Poll until the hard-restart transition operation has completed
